%3EShazeer%20was%20a%20key%20part%20of%20Google's%20early%20LLM%20development%20efforts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENoam%20Shazeer%2C%20a%20co-lead%20at%20Gemini%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20Character.AI%20is%20leaving%20Google%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgary-marcus-ai-openai-ipo-nvidia-orcl-nvda-crwv-02026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejoin%20OpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20latest%20AI%20talent%20war%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20X%20post%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Shazeer%20announced%20his%20departure%20and%20said%20he%20looks%20forward%20to%20working%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Bexceptional%20team%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20ChatGPT%20maker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20difficult%20decision%20to%20move%20on.%20I'm%20incredibly%20proud%20of%20the%20amazing%20team%20at%20Google%20and%20everything%20we've%20built%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Shazeer%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20an%20honor%20and%20a%20pleasure%20to%20work%20with%20all%20of%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Wednesday%20X%20post%2C%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20said%20Shazeer%20%26quot%3Bis%20one%20of%20the%20people%20I%20have%20most%20wanted%20to%20work%20with%20since%20the%20very%20beginning%20of%20openai.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.x.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Enoam%20is%20one%20of%20the%20people%20I%20have%20most%20wanted%20to%20work%20with%20since%20the%20very%20beginning%20of%20openai.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3Eonly%20took%2010%20years.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3Ei%20think%20it%20will%20be%20worth%20the%20wait!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FHj2fjCywjv%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FHj2fjCywjv%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Sam%20Altman%20(%40sama)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fsama%2Fstatus%2F2067427421083652131%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2018%2C%202026%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Gemini%20co-lead%20joined%20Google%20in%202000%20and%20stayed%20with%20the%20company%2C%20aside%20from%20a%20three-year%20period%20when%20he%20left%20to%20cofound%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-character-ai-settling-lawsuits-teen-suicides-new-york-texas-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echatbot-building%20startup%20Character.AI%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%202024%2C%20the%20search%20giant%20rehired%20the%20founders%20and%20paid%20for%20non-exclusive%20rights%20to%20use%20the%20startup's%20technology.%20Character.AI%20remains%20a%20separate%20legal%20entity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20reported%20that%20Google%20paid%20Character.AI%20%242.7%20billion%20for%20a%20special%20deal%20that%20gave%20Google%20access%20to%20the%20startup's%20technology%2C%20and%20an%20agreement%20that%20Shazeer%20would%20have%20to%20work%20for%20Google%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShazeer%20was%20a%20key%20part%20of%20Google's%20early%20AI%20development%20efforts.%20A%202017%20paper%20he%20coauthored%20is%20largely%20seen%20as%20the%20kickstarter%20to%20present-day%20large%20language%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShazeer's%20move%20to%20the%20IPO-bound%20company%20is%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20series%20of%20top-talent%20reshuffles%20at%20AI%20heavyweights.%20Labs%2C%20including%20OpenAI%2C%20Google%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20Anthropic%2C%20are%20offering%20top%20researchers%20and%20engineers%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-paying-ai-internships-fellowships-residencies-openai-anthropic-meta-google-2025-12%23anthropic-safety-fellow-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenormous%20pay%20packages%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20devising%20complex%20acqui-hire%20deals%20to%20incentivize%20them%20to%20make%20the%20jump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20artic