0an%20Apple%20event%20in%20New%20York%2C%20US%2C%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20March%204%2C%202026.%20Apple%20Inc.%20this%20week%20unveiled%20a%20slate%20of%20new%20products%2C%20including%20the%20%24599%20MacBook%20Neo%20-%20its%20first%20true%20low-end%20laptop%20-%20and%20the%20iPhone%2017e.%20The%20company%20also%20announced%20updated%20versions%20of%20the%20MacBook%20Pro%2C%20MacBook%20Air%2C%20Studio%20Display%20and%20iPad%20Air.%20Photographer%3A%20Adam%20Gray%2FBloomberg%20via%20Getty%20Images%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3316f04074dae0e204542f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223719%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EApple%20CEO%20Tim%20Cook%20warned%20of%20price%20hikes%20due%20to%20a%20global%20memory%20chip%20shortage.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EApple's%20Tim%20Cook%20warned%20of%20price%20hikes%20due%20to%20a%20global%20memory%20chip%20shortage%2C%20which%20is%20spiking%20costs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERising%20demand%20for%20memory%20chips%20for%20AI%20models%20is%20squeezing%20supplies%20for%20everyday%20gadgets%20like%20phones.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMacBook%20prices%20rose%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20and%20more%20increases%20are%20expected%20as%20memory%20costs%20climb.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you've%20been%20eyeing%20a%20new%20iPhone%2C%20MacBook%2C%20or%20iPad%2C%20waiting%20to%20buy%20one%20could%20get%20more%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20culprit%20isn't%20tariffs%20or%20flashy%20new%20features.%20It's%20memory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECEO%20Tim%20Cook%20told%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20published%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20Apple%20could%20raise%20prices%20on%20some%20of%20its%20products%20as%20a%20global%20shortage%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmemory-shortage-chips-cost-laptop-pc-prices-increase-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ememory%20chips%3C%2Fa%3E%20drives%20up%20costs%20across%20the%20consumer%20electronics%20industry%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20price%20increases%20are%20unavoidable%2C%26quot%3B%20Cook%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20doing%20our%20best%20to%20mitigate%20the%20huge%20increases%20that%20are%20being%20passed%20to%20us%2C%20and%20we've%20been%20trying%20to%20shield%20our%20customers%20from%20the%20increases%2C%20but%20the%20situation%20has%20become%20unsustainable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20less%20supply%20at%20a%20time%20when%20consumers%20want%20devices%20and%20the%20memory%20guys%20are%20passing%20along%20huge%20price%20increases%2C%26quot%3B%20Cook%20added.%20%26quot%3BWe%20definitely%20need%20memory%20pricing%20and%20supply%20to%20return%20to%20reasonable%20levels%20for%20consumer%20products.%20That's%20the%20bottom%20line.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECook%2C%20who%20called%20the%20price%20fluctuation%20in%20memory%20%26quot%3Ba%20hundred-year%20flood%2C%26quot%3B%20did%20not%20specify%20when%20the%20increases%20would%20arrive%2C%20how%20large%20they%20would%20be%2C%20or%20which%20products%20would%20be%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20warning%20comes%20as%20AI%20companies%20race%20to%20build%20ever-larger%20models%20and%20snap%20up%20huge%20quantities%20of%20memory%20chips%20used%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-soaring-memory-costs-ai-systems-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edata%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20surge%20in%20demand%20is%20squeezing%20supplies%20of%20the%20DRAM%20and%20NAND%20chips%20that%20power%20everyday%20gadgets%2C%20from%20laptops%20to%20smartphones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20raised%20prices%20on%20its%20latest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-macbook-air-pro-m5-prices-increase-memory-shortage-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMacBook%20lineup%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20year.%20The%2014-inch%20MacBook%20Pro%20with%20the%20M5%20Pro%20chip%20jumped%20to%20%242%2C199%20from%20%241%2C999%2C%20and%20