re%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJeff%20Bezos%20said%20AI%20will%20create%20job%20opportunities%2C%20not%20eliminate%20them%2C%20at%20VivaTech%20in%20Paris.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBezos%20said%20AI%20would%20unlock%20innovation%20and%20create%20%26quot%3Bendless%26quot%3B%20demand%20for%20builders%20and%20entrepreneurs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBezos%20AI's%20potential%20to%20advance%20space%20exploration%20and%20move%20heavy%20industries%20off%20Earth.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezos-life-career-education%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJeff%20Bezos%3C%2Fa%3E%20predicts%20AI%20will%20do%20the%20opposite%20of%20what%20most%20people%20fear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20VivaTech%20conference%20in%20Paris%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworked-with-jeff-bezos-amazon-early-2000s-built-career-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmazon%20founder%3C%2Fa%3E%20pushed%20back%20on%20growing%20fears%20that%20AI%20will%20eliminate%20large%20numbers%20of%20jobs.%20Instead%2C%20he%20said%20that%20the%20technology%20will%20unlock%20new%20opportunities%20and%20increase%20demand%20for%20people%20capable%20of%20turning%20ideas%20into%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20concern%20that%20many%20people%20have%2C%20including%20many%20smart%20people%2C%20that%20AI%20is%20going%20to%20make%20humans%20redundant%2C%26quot%3B%20Bezos%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20totally%20disagree%20with%20this%20point%20of%20view%2C%20and%20I%20think%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20AI%20is%20going%20to%20create%20a%20labor%20shortage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20an%20endless%20set%20of%20things%20to%20invent%2C%26quot%3B%20Bezos%20added.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20limited%20not%20by%20our%20imaginations%20but%20by%20what%20we%20can%20actually%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20workers%20and%20economists%20have%20warned%20that%20advances%20in%20AI%20could%20automate%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20tasks%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpoll-americans-worry-ai-make-jobs-obsolete-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edisplace%20employees%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20Reuters%2FIpsos%20poll%20released%20in%20early%20June%20found%20that%20about%20half%20of%20Americans%20worry%20that%20AI%20could%20threaten%20jobs%20and%20household%20incomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Bezos'%20view%2C%20however%2C%20AI%20could%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20turn%20concepts%20into%20reality%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20could%20create%20demand%20for%20more%20builders%2C%20creators%2C%20and%20entrepreneurs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20promise%20you%20every%20single%20person%20in%20this%20audience%20has%20had%20an%20idea%20for%20a%20new%20business%20or%20a%20new%20product%20or%20a%20new%20device%20that%20they%20wish%20they%20could%20manufacture%2C%20and%20that%20idea%20stayed%20in%20your%20head%20and%20went%20nowhere%2C%26quot%3B%20Bezos%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAnd%20the%20reason%20it%20stayed%20in%20your%20head%20and%20went%20nowhere%20is%20because%20it's%20too%20hard%20to%20do%2C%20and%20it%20wasn't%20worth%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20can%20accelerate%20the%20dream%20build%20loop%2C%20all%20of%20the%20ideas%20will%20then%20become%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20Bezos%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20we%20end%20up%20being%20limited%20not%20by%20our%20capabilities%2C%20but%20by%20our%20imaginations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20example%2C%20said%20Bezos%2C%20is%20what%20AI%20could%20do%20for%20space%20exploration%2C%20potentially%20moving%20heavy%20industry%20off%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20space%20travel%20gets%20reliable%20enough%20and%20inexpensive%20enough%2C%20and%20we%20can%20get%20materials%20from%20%E2%81%A0asteroids%20and%20near-Earth%20objects%20and%20the%20moon%2C%20then%20this%20garden%20planet%20can%20be%20returned%20to%20its%20pre-Industrial%20Revolution%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20Bezos%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBezos%20isn't%20the%20only%20billionaire%20imagining%20a%20future%20beyond%20Earth.%20Ahead%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-10-largest-public-offerings-ranked-by-proceeds-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESpaceX's%20IPO%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20week%2C%20Elon%20Musk%20described%20a%20world%20where%20humans%20live%20in%20lunar%20and%20Martian%20cities%2C%20AI%20data%20centers%20operate%20in%20space%2C%20and%20moon%20vacations%20become%20commonplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezos-ai-will-create-labor-shortage-not-mass-unemployment-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781732195000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a32f7c12bbd1d834ef251ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezos-ai-will-create-labor-shortage-not-mass-unemployment-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20fears%20mount%20that%20AI%20could%20erase%20jobs%2C%20the%20Amazon%20founder%20pushed%20back%20against%20the%20idea%20that%20AI%20would%20make%20humans%20redundant.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22katherineli%40insider.com%20(Katherine%20Li)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A97%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Angelina%20Jolie%20on%20Her%20Kids%20%E2%80%98Encouraging%E2%80%99%20Her%20to%20%E2%80%98Get%20Out%20and%20Do%20Things%E2%80%99%3A%20%E2%80%98My%20Fighting%20Spirit%20Is%20Finally%20Back%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781732087000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236784317%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20%E2%80%9CCouture%2C%E2%80%9D%20Angelina%20Jolie%20plays%20Maxine%2C%20a%20low-budget%20horror%20movie%20director%20juggling%20a%20film%20commission%20from%20a%20French%20luxury%20fashion%20house%20and%20be