%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20splurging%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fupgrading-premium-plus-united-long-flight-international-iworth-it-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnited's%20Premium%20Plus%20seats%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20a%20recent%20trip%20to%20South%20Korea%2C%20I%20gained%20a%20new%20appreciation%20for%20what%20the%20extra%20cash%20(or%20miles)%20can%20get%20you%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flong-flight-worst-things-to-do-mistakes-flight-attendant-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elong-haul%20flights%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20I%20discovered%20that%20the%20value%20of%20sitting%20toward%20the%20front%20of%20the%20plane%20goes%20beyond%20a%20bigger%20seat%20and%20more%20attentive%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflew-premium-economy-norse-airlines-upgrade-worth-it-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFlying%20premium%3C%2Fa%3E%20ultimately%20helped%20me%20arrive%20at%20my%20destination%20feeling%20refreshed%2C%20well-rested%2C%20and%20better%20able%20to%20beat%20jet%20lag%2C%20which%20saved%20the%20first%20day%20or%20two%20of%20my%20vacation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20for%20a%20recent%20trip%20from%20Baltimore%20to%20Copenhagen%20and%20back%20with%20a%20layover%20in%20Reykjav%C3%ADk%20both%20ways%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20fly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflying-saga-premium-class-on-icelandair-review-worth-it-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIcelandair's%20Saga%20Premium%20class%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20upgraded%20round-trip%20ticket%20cost%20%242%2C637%20(several%20hundred%20dollars%20more%20than%20I%20would've%20paid%20for%20economy)%20and%20included%20four%20flights%20totaling%20just%20over%2019%20hours.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20they%20didn't%20disappoint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESaga%20Premium%20is%20not%20a%20true%20business%20class%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20big%20upgrade%20from%20economy.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22View%20of%20two%20IcelandAir%20Saga%20Premium%20seats%20next%20to%20plane%20window%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2ae4ff50aa6577af8717da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJamie%20Davis%20Smith%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIcelandair's%20Saga%20Premium%20is%20the%20Nordic%20airline's%20highest%20offering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20also%20say%20it's%20the%20airline's%20version%20of%20business%20class%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%20sure%20I%20agree.%20Notably%2C%20Saga%20Premium%20features%20large%20reclining%20seats%20rather%20than%20the%20coveted%20lie-flat%20ones%20that%20most%20business%20classes%20offer%20on%20long-haul%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20seats%20here%20were%20nothing%20to%20scoff%20at%20and%20felt%20like%20a%20big%20upgrade%20from%20any%20economy%20seat%20I've%20tried.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20this%20plane%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icelandair.com%2Fabout%2Four-fleet%2Fboeing-737-max%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoeing%20737%20Max%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20premium%20seats%20were%2020.5%20inches%20wide%20with%20a%2040-inch%20pitch%20compared%20to%20economy%20seats%2C%20which%20were%2017.2%20inches%20wide%20with%20a%2031-%20to%2032-inch%20pitch.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20wide%20premium%20seats%20were%20grouped%20in%20pairs%20and%20located%20at%20the%20front%20of%20the%20plane.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22View%20of%20screenback%2C%20legroom%20of%20seat%20in%20IcelandAir%20Saga%20Premium%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2ae50024b3540ad29c20cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJamie%20Davis%20Smith%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20seats%20were%20in%20a%20two-by-two%20configuration%20on%20my%20flight%2C%20and%20I%20was%20in%20the%20aisle.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20would've%20been%20nice%20being%20able%20to%20lie%20down%2C%20my%20seat%20felt%20spacious%20and%20incredibly%20comfortable%20with%20a%20deep%20recline%2C%20a%20footrest%2C%20and%20ample%20legroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20these%20upgrades%2C%20I%20slept%20more%20than%20I%20thought%20possible%20on%20my%20way%20to%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20had%20a%20large%20seatback%20screen%20packed%20with%20in-flight%20entertainment%20options%2C%20plus%20access%20to%20complimentary%20WiFi%20for%20up%20to%20two%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20food%20was%20delicious%2C%20and%20I%20loved%20the%20in-air%20dining%20experience.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Plates%20of%20food%20on%20tray%20table%20in%20IcelandAir%20Saga%20Premium%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2ae5006588b2a09a7c6baf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJamie%20Davis%20Smith%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20each%20meal%20service%2C%20I%20received%20a%20printed%20menu%20from%20which%20I%20could%20choose%20what%20to%20eat%20during%20my%20flight.%20I%20appreciated%20that%20some%20options%20were%20Nordic-inspired.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20my%20meals%20were%20fantastic%2C%20but%20dinner%20was%20a%20highlight.%20The%20three-course%20meal%20started%20with%20a%20salad%20and%20bread%20served%20with%20whipped%20butter%20topped%20with%20Icelandic%20blueberry%20salt.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20my%20main%2C%20I%20chose%20a%20vegetarian%20option%20that%20included%20plant-based%20patties%20and%20roasted%20carrots.%20I%20ended%20my%20meal%20with%20a%20rhubarb%20crumble%20for%20dessert.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFood%20was%20served%20on%20porcelain%20plates%20with%20metal%20silverware%20on%20a%20tray-sized%20tablecloth%2C%20which%20elevated%20the%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20huge%20upgrade%20from%20the%20typical%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdifference-between-flight-meal-service-business-economy-class-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emeal%20service%20on%20airplanes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20a%20flight%20attendant%20usually%20shoves%20a%20plastic%20tray%20into%20my%20hands%20along%20with%20a%20half-filled%20cup%20of%20soda.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%2C%20my%20in-air%20dining%20experience%20truly%20made%20me%20feel%20like%20I%20was%20in%20a%20restaurant%20in%20the%20sky.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20also%20loved%20having%20unlimited%20access%20to%20drinks%20throughout%20my%20flight.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hand%20holding%20glass%20of%20alcohol%20%20on%20IcelandAir%20plane%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2ae4ff50aa6577af8717db%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJamie%20Davis%20Smith%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlcoholic%20drinks%2C%20including%20specialty%20spirits%20from%20Iceland%2C%20were%20included%20with%20my%20ticket.%20They%20looked%20great%2C%20but%20I%20stuck%20to%20zero-proof%20options.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20especially%20appreciated%20the%20easy%20access%20to%20caffeine%20on%20my%20flight%20home%2C%20when%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20stay%20awake%20until%20landing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBeing%20able%20to%20access%20Icelandair's%20Saga%20Lounge%20during%20my%20layovers%20was%20a%20nice%20bonus%2C%20too.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Display%20of%20buffet-style%20food%20in%20airport%20lounge%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2ae50024b3540ad29c20ce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJamie%20Davis%20Smith%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20I%20have%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3