-travel-2019-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etry%20to%20fly%20carry-on-only%3C%2Fa%3E%20wherever%20possible%2C%20I%20do%20occasionally%20check%20bags%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20did%20so%20on%20this%20trip%20since%20my%20packing%20list%20was%20so%20extensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20up%20to%20two%20complimentary%20checked%20bags%20with%20my%20ticket%20was%20a%20nice%20perk%2C%20since%20I%20usually%20have%20to%20pay%20extra%20to%20bring%20a%20full-sized%20suitcase%20on%20a%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20benefit%20of%20flying%20Saga%20Premium%20is%20getting%20priority%20check-in%20and%20boarding.%20Check-in%20lines%20for%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ficelandair-flights-to-iceland-review-food-photos-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIcelandair%20flights%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20long%2C%20so%20it%20was%20nice%20to%20have%20access%20to%20a%20shorter%20one%20for%20premium%20passengers.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPriority%20boarding%20was%20nice%2C%20too%2C%20since%20I%20didn't%20have%20to%20fight%20for%20overhead%20space%20for%20my%20carry-on.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20disembarking%2C%20I%20usually%20stand%20up%20as%20soon%20as%20we%20stop%2C%20anxiously%20waiting%20for%20other%20passengers%20to%20gather%20their%20luggage%20and%20clear%20the%20aisle.%20Instead%20of%20waiting%20at%20the%20back%2C%20though%2C%20I%20got%20to%20get%20up%20right%20away%20and%20be%20one%20of%20the%20first%20people%20off%20the%20plane.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20helped%20me%20get%20through%20immigration%20in%20Europe%20and%20the%20United%20States%20even%20faster%20because%20I%20wasn't%20stuck%20behind%20passengers%20who%20deplaned%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAll%20in%20all%2C%20this%20premium%20class%20left%20me%20feeling%20impressed.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20Jamie%20Davis%20Smith%20smiling%20next%20to%20%26quot%3BExit%20to%20Iceland%26quot%3B%20sign%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.