g%20width%3D%5C%224728%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CHINA%20-%202023%2F11%2F03%3A%20In%20this%20photo%20illustration%2C%20the%20American%20multinational%20mass%20media%20and%20entertainment%20The%20Walt%20Disney%20Company%20or%20also%20called%20Disney%20logo%20seen%20displayed%20on%20a%20smartphone%20with%20an%20Artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20chip%20and%20symbol%20in%20the%20background.%20(Photo%20Illustration%20by%20Budrul%20Chukrut%2FSOPA%20Images%2FLightRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images)%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a32f630564c774507cd3f7a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223146%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDisney%20is%20making%20progress%20on%20using%20AI%20to%20make%20ads%20for%20clients.%3Cp%3EIllustration%20by%20Budrul%20Chukrut%2FSOPA%20Images%2FLightRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDisney%20plans%20to%20roll%20out%20AI-generated%20TV%20ads%20in%20July%20with%20small-%20to%20medium-sized%20businesses%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20Disney%20exec%20recently%20highlighted%20AI%20ads%20as%20a%20key%20area%20of%20progress%20in%20his%20team's%20strategy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EQuality%20control%20in%20AI%20ads%20is%20still%20an%20industry%20concern.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-disney-tech-employees-are-using-ai-claude-cursor-tokens-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDisney's%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20ad%20push%20is%20picking%20up%20steam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20is%20preparing%20to%20launch%20a%20beta%20version%20of%20a%20tool%20for%20AI-generated%20TV%20ads%20in%20July%2C%20a%20Disney%20exec%20said%20at%20an%20internal%20meeting%2C%20according%20to%20an%20audio%20recording%20shared%20with%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20entertainment%20giant%20originally%20shared%20news%20of%20the%20tool%20in%20January%2C%20as%20part%20of%20a%20broader%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewaltdisneycompany.com%2Fnews%2Ftech-data-showcase-advertising-2026%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECES%20announcement%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20upcoming%20tech-driven%20features%20for%20advertisers.%20Other%20major%20ad%20sellers%2C%20such%20as%20Google%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20TikTok%2C%20have%20also%20rolled%20out%20AI%20ad-generation%20tools%20for%20advertisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdam%20Smith%2C%20the%20chief%20product%20and%20technology%20officer%20for%20Disney%20Entertainment%20and%20ESPN%2C%20shared%20the%20timing%20update%20with%20employees%20during%20a%20product%20meeting%20last%20week.%20He%20said%20the%20AI%20tool%20can%20generate%20scripts%2C%20video%2C%20and%20music%2C%20and%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20clearest%20areas%20where%20we're%20really%20making%20traction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20said%20the%20ad%20tool%20was%20particularly%20geared%20to%20small%20and%20medium-sized%20advertisers%20that%20don't%20have%20video%20assets.%20In%20its%20earlier%20announcement%2C%20Disney%20touted%20the%20tool's%20ability%20to%20help%20brands%20create%20connected%20TV%20spots%20using%20their%20existing%20creative%20assets%2C%20letting%20them%20customize%20them%20by%20factors%20like%20audience%20and%20context%20while%20still%20providing%20a%20level%20of%20human%20oversight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20said%20it%20would%20eventually%20be%20available%20through%20Disney's%20self-service%20ad%20platform%2C%20a%20dashboard%20where%20advertisers%20can%20manage%20and%20run%20ad%20campaigns%20on%20Disney%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20think%20of%20this%20as%20everything%20from%20creation%20of%20scripts%2C%20video%2C%20and%20music%2C%20all%20that%20is%20in%20a%20single%20orchestrated%20workflow%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%20recording.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20week%20they%20send%20me%20examples%20of%20these%2C%20and%20I%20will%20say%20every%20week%20the%20examples%20get%20better%20and%20better.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAshwin%20Navin%2C%20CEO%20of%20Samba%20TV%2C%20an%20ads%20measurement%20service%2C%20said%20a%20video%20ad-generation%20tool%20like%20Disney's%20could%20open%20the%20company%20up%20to%20advertisers%20with%20smaller%20budgets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENavin%20said%20these%20advertisers%20don't%20have%20the%20budget%20to%20pay%20a%20%26quot%3Bcreative%20agency%20to%20come%20up%20with%20the%20perfect%2030-second%20video.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlicia%20Weaver%2C%20VP%20of%20media%20activation%20at%20the%20media%20agency%20Mediassociates%2C%20said%20she's%20started%20talking%20to%20clients%20about%20the%20Disney%20tool%20and%20sees%20it%20as%20a%20way%20to%20help%20advertisers%20customize%20their%20connected%20TV%20ads%20for%20different%20audiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20takes%20time%20to%20create%20different%20versions%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSomething%20that%20helps%20facilitate%20that%20in%20a%20more%20turnkey%20fashion%20is%20definitely%20a%20benefit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdvertisers%20have%20moved%20from%20the%20excitement%20phase%20of%20seeing%20AI's%20promise%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcpg-marketers-using-ai-ad-testing-to-video-production-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esave%20time%20and%20money%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20fear%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrands-reject-ai-aerie-heineken-polaroid-marketing-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econsumer%20backlash%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20so-called%20slop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMindful%20of%20that%20shift%2C%20Weaver%20said%20she%20wanted%20to%20learn%20how%20Disney%20would%20ensure%20the%20ads%20meet%20brands'%20quality-control%20expectations%2C%20among%20other%20questions%2C%20before%20recommending%20the%20ad%20tool%20to%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20reached%20the%20point%20with%20AI%20where%20clients%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20their%20brand%20is%20represented%20correctly%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20more%20scrutiny%20on%20AI%20now%20that%20we've%20seen%20what%20it%20can%20do.%20It's%20not%20a%20shiny%20new%20object%20anymore.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisneys-ai-generated-tv-ads-set-to-launch-in-july-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781727001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a32f6912bbd1d834ef2519d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisneys-ai-generated-tv-ads-set-to-launch-in-july-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Disney%20is%20launching%20AI-generated%20TV%20ads%20in%20July.%20A%20new%20tool%20generates%20scripts%2C%20music%2C%20and%20video%20to%20streamline%20ad%20creation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jfaris%40businessinsider.com%20(James%20Faris%2CLucia%20Moses)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Latine%20Immigrant%20Representation%20Drops%20to%2025%25%20Across%20Scripted%20TV%3A%20Industry%20%E2%80%98Cannot%20Rely%20on%20a%20Few%20Programs%20to%20Represent%20the%20Whole%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781726720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236783990%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Representation%20for%20Latine%20immigrants%20on%20TV%20has%20hit%20a%20new%20low%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20from%20Define%20American%2C%20conducted%20in%20partnership%20with%20USC%E2%80%99s%20Norman%20Lear%20Center.%20The%20%E2%80%9CChange%20the%20Narrative%2C%20Change%20the%20World%E2%80%9D%20report%20assessed%20201%20immigrant%20characters%20across%2080%20episodes%20of%2062%20scripted%20series%2C%20all%20of%20which%20aired%20between%20July%202023%20and%20June%202025.%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Matthew%20Minton%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kevin%20Warsh%20looks%20ready%20to%20rewrite%20the%20Fed's%20rules%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22kevin%20warsh%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3148629ab49a561172042a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKevin%20Warsh%2C%20the%20Fed's%20new%20chair%2C%20has%20a%20reputation%20for%20being%20tough%20on%20inflation.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EKevin%20Warsh%20succeeded%20Jerome%20Powell%20as%20chair%20of%20the%20central%20bank.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Fed%20opted%20to%20hold%20rates%20steady%20in%20Warsh's%20first%20meeting%2C%20as%20expected.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWarsh%20seems%20poised%20to%20change%20some%20long-standing%20FOMC%20traditions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkevin-warsh-first-fomc-fed-meeting-interest-rates-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKevin%20Warsh%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20taken%20the%20podium%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he%20plans%20to%20make%20some%20major%20changes%20at%20the%20central%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Open%20Market%20Committee%20opted%20to%20hold%20rates%20steady%20at%20its%20June%20meeting%2C%20the%20first%20with%20former%20Wall%20Street%20executive%20Warsh%20as%20chair.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-rates-interest-yield-kevin-warsh-trump-federal-reserve-chair-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFOMC%20leaders%3C%2Fa%3E%20voted%20unanimously%20for%20the%20hold%2C%20with%20half%20predicting%20at%20least%20one%20rate%20hike%20by%20year's%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20stuck%20out%20from%20Warsh's%20first%20press%20conference%20wasn't%20monetary%20policy%3B%20it%20was%20how%20much%20he%20plans%20to%20change%20long-standing%20Fed%20traditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22920d4993-89a9-4dbd-9372-3d66eeddc31c%5C%22%3EFewer%20forecasts%2C%20more%20task%20forces%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWarsh%20chose%20to%20eliminate%20the%20Fed's%20forward%20guidance%20in%20June's%20statement.%20That%20statement%20was%20bare-bones%20compared%20to%20his%20predecessors'%2C%20with%20limited%20detail%20on%20how%20and%20why%20the%20Fed%20made%20its%20decision%2C%20a%20style%20that%20had%20been%20customary%20under%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharts-fed-chair-jerome-powell-jobs-inflation-interest-rates-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJerome%20Powell's%20tenure%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20still%20published%20a%20quarterly%20dot%20plot%20showing%20FOMC%20members'%20estimates%20for%20where%20interest%20rates%20would%20end%20up%20in%20the%20coming%20years%20%E2%80%94%20though%20Warsh%20said%20he%20abstained%20from%20submitting%20his%20own%20prediction%20for%20future%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20what%20economic%20predictions%20the%20FOMC%20will%20make%20going%20forward.%20While%20critics%20worry%20that%20this%20approach%20will%20reduce%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjerome-powell-worlds-central-bankers-rallying-around-federal-reserve-chair-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecentral%20bank's%20transparency%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Warsh%20hopes%20markets%20will%20rely%20less%20on%20Fed%20moves.%20He%20notably%20didn't%20talk%20much%20about%20Fed%20independence%2C%20which%20has%20been%20a%20key%20topic%20at%20previous%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20financial%20markets%20perform%20best%20when%20they%20react%20to%20incoming%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20more%20that%20markets%20are%20paying%20attention%20to%20what's%20happening%20in%20the%20real%20economy%20%E2%80%94%20what's%20good%20data%2C%20and%20what's%20less%20good%20data%20%E2%80%94%20the%20more%20financial%20markets%20can%20price%20what%20they%20believe%20is%20the%20most%20likely%20and%20what%20is%20the%20tail%20risk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20forecasts%2C%20Warsh%20said%20he%20wants%20to%20reevaluate%20the%20data%20the%20Fed%20uses%20to%20make%20decisions%2C%20relying%20more%20on%20real-time%20numbers%20and%20less%20on%20%26quot%3Bechoes%20of%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20like%20the%20often-revised%20monthly%20jobs%20report.%20He%20added%20that%20trends%20matter%20more%20than%20specific%20numbers%2C%20and%20he%20wants%20to%20phase%20out%20the%20%26quot%3Bold-fashioned%20survey%20methods%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20central%20bank%20uses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20bring%20the%20Fed%20into%20the%20future%2C%20Warsh%20has%20one%20shining%20solution%3A%20Task%20forces.%20He%20said%20he%20is%20appointing%20independent%20groups%20of%20economic%20experts%2C%20partnered%20with%20FOMC%20leaders%2C%20to%20oversee%20his%20new%20initiatives.%20The%20task%20forces%20will%20focus%20on%20the%20Fed's%20handling%20of%20data%2C%20jobs%20and%20productivity%2C%20communication%2C%20inflation%2C%20and%20the%20balance%20sheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20task%20forces%20were%20a%20recurring%20theme%20throughout%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20press%20conference.%20Per%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tradingview.com%2Fnews%2Fmacenews%3Ad31687211094b%3A0-transcript-fed-chair-warsh-says-wants-changes-appoints-five-task-forces-but-will-keep-2-inflation-target%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunofficial%20early%20transcript%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Warsh%20said%20the%20phrase%20%26quot%3Btask%20force%26quot%3B%2024%20times%20in%20the%20roughly%2042-minute%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20chair%20said%20he%20is%20impressed%20by%20the%20committee%20and%20feels%20confident%20in%20the%20Fed's%20ability%20to%20fulfill%20both%20sides%20of%20its%20dual%20mandate.%20He%20added%20that%20his%20plan%20doesn't%20mean%20outsourcing%20decisions%2C%20but%20he%20expects%20more%20structural%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20task%20force%20for%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Warsh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkevin-warsh-first-fomc-interest-rate-meeting-biggest-takeaways-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781726666000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a314a5a9ab49a5611720444%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkevin-warsh-first-fomc-interest-rate-meeting-biggest-takeaways-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trump%20pick%20Kevin%20Warsh%20oversaw%20his%20first%20meeting%20as%20chair%20of%20the%20Fed.%20Here%20are%20Business%20Insider's%20biggest%20takeaways.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22allisonkelly%40businessinsider.com%20(Allie%20Kelly)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Other%20Countries%20Have%20Ballistic%20Missiles%2C%20Unfair%20If%20Iran%20Does%20Not%3A%20Trump%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20it%20would%20be%20unfair%20for%20Iran%20not%20to%20have%20ballistic%20missiles%20if%20other%20countries%20have%20them.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781726468000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fother-countries-have-ballistic-missiles-unfair-if-iran-does-not-donald-trump-11651719%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20it%20would%20be%20unfair%20for%20Iran%20not%20to%20have%20ballistic%20missiles%20if%20other%20countries%20have%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A96%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fother-countries-have-ballistic-missiles-unfair-if-iran-does-not-donald-trump-11651719%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fother-countries-have-ballistic-missiles-unfair-if-iran-does-not-donald-trump