%20beautifying%20the%20landmark%20and%20addressing%20maintenance%20issues%2C%20including%20leaks%20and%20algae%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20within%20days%2C%20the%20pool%20was%20a%20bright%20chartreuse%20green%20%E2%80%94%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225757%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22WASHINGTON%2C%20DC%20-%20JUNE%2016%3A%20A%20duckling%20swims%20through%20algae%20in%20the%20newly%20repainted%20Lincoln%20Memorial%20Reflecting%20Pool%20on%20the%20National%20Mall%20on%20June%2016%2C%202026%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC.%20The%20Trump%20Administration%20spent%20%2416%20million%20on%20a%20no-bid%20contract%20to%20have%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20pool%20painted%20%26quot%3BAmerican%20flag%20blue%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20seams%20resealed%20as%20part%20of%20an%20effort%20to%20repair%20Washington%20landmarks%20in%20for%20preparation%20the%20country's%20250th%20birthday%20this%20summer.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a32c98a564c774507cd38d0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224318%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlgae%20has%20bloomed%20at%20the%20Lincoln%20Memorial%20Reflecting%20Pool%20%E2%80%94%20again.%3Cp%3EChip%20Somodevilla%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2233d3b60b-f386-4866-9876-e9cf2b0f9225%5C%22%3EThe%20new%20blue-colored%20pool%20was%20revealed%20earlier%20this%20month%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20resurfacing%20work%20was%20completed%20on%20June%203%2C%20and%20the%20pool%20refilling%20began%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESatellite%20photos%20taken%20in%20March%2C%20before%20the%20renovation%20began%2C%20showed%20a%20green%20pool%20due%20to%20widespread%20algae%20growth%2C%20while%20images%20taken%20on%20June%207%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20president%20said%20the%20project%20was%20complete%2C%20showed%20a%20darker%20color.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Horizontal%20split%20image%20of%20satellite%20footage%20showing%20the%20before%20and%20after%20of%20the%20Lincoln%20Memorial%20Reflecting%20Pool%20along%20the%20National%20Mall%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2b0bc26588b2a09a7c6d62%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESatellite%20images%20showed%20the%20before%20(top)%20and%20after%20(bottom)%20of%20the%20renovation%20project.%3Cp%3EVantor%2FHandout%20via%20REUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20week%20later%2C%20algae%20was%20visible%20again.%20Photos%20taken%20on%20June%2016%20showed%20the%20pool%20had%20returned%20to%20its%20former%20green%20hue%2C%20which%20could%20be%20seen%20from%20the%20sky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222493%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22WASHINGTON%2C%20DC%20-%20JUNE%2016%3A%20Water%20in%20the%20Lincoln%20Memorial%20Reflecting%20Pool%20(lower%20right)%20is%20shown%20from%20a%20departing%20flight%20from%20Ronald%20Reagan%20National%20Airport%20as%20algae%20continues%20to%20bloom%20following%20the%20completion%20of%20recent%20renovations%20on%20June%2016%2C%202026%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a318f6f564c774507cd30c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221870%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20pool's%20return%20to%20green%20could%20be%20seen%20from%20this%20airplane%20picture%20taken%20on%20June%2016.%3Cp%3EWin%20McNamee%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b3d75cf9-a295-499c-9cbe-e29866ba7fbb%5C%22%3EWhy%20the%20pool%20keeps%20turning%20green%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20broad%2C%20shallow%20pool%20has%20long%20been%20plagued%20by%20algal%20blooms%2C%20a%20problem%20exacerbated%20by%20summer%20heat%20and%20the%20Tidal%20Basin's%20algae-prone%20water%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Ftrump-reflecting-pool-renovation-1235f9417697bb2e1f56e14e4d2214de%23%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAssociated%20Press%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStructural%20issues%20date%20back%20to%20the%20pool's%20construction%2C%20as%20it%20was%20built%20on%20unstable%20mudflats%20that%20have%20caused%20cracks%20and%20leaks%20over%20the%20past%20century%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Finteractive%2F2026%2F05%2F31%2Fus%2Ftrump-reflecting-pool-problems.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20resurfacing%20didn't%20address%20the%20underlying%20flaws%20with%20the%20pool's%20construction%2C%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20reported.%20Instead%2C%20it%20coated%20the%20slabs%20of%20concrete%20between%20which%20water%20leaks%20with%20a%20blue-tinted%20sealant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2026%2F06%2F16%2Fpolitics%2Flincoln-reflecting-pool-algae%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInterior%20communications%20director%3C%2Fa%3E%20Kate%20Martin%20told%20CNN%20that%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bfixed%20the%20Reflecting%20Pool%20for%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20unlike%20what%20she%20called%20%26quot%3Bthe%20failed%20and%20extremely%20costly%20attempt%20by%20Obama%20and%20Biden.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20you%20are%20seeing%20%5Bnow%5D%20is%20residual%20algae%20from%20the%20supply%20lines%2C%26quot%3B%20Martin%20said%20on%20June%2010%2C%20calling%20the%20new%20green%20hue%20part%20of%20the%20pool's%20%26quot%3Bnormal%20startup%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20workers%20on%20the%20landmark%20continue%20fighting%20algae%20growth%20and%20have%20been%20seen%20skimming%20the%20water%2C%20vacuuming%20the%20pool%20floor%2C%20using%20ozone%20nanobubbles%2C%20and%20dumping%20hydrogen%20peroxide%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20restore%20it%20to%20its%20intended%20%26quot%3BAmerican%20Flag%20Blue%26quot%3B%20color.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22National%20Park%20Service%20workers%20push%20algae%20towards%20an%20aeration%20area%20in%20the%20center%20of%20the%20Lincoln%20Memorial%20Reflecting%20Pool%20following%20the%20completion%20of%20recent%20renovations%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20on%20June%2014%2C%202026%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3190424074dae0e20443e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWorkers%20have%20been%20spotted%20skimming%20algae%20off%20the%20pool%20since%20its%20reopening.%3Cp%3EKen%20CEDENO%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225cd4566d-6169-42a9-9361-e65409045c98%5C%22%3EThe%20makeover%20had%20attracted%20criticism%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20renovation%20is%20just%20one%20of%20the%20many%20projects%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20undertaken%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-second-term-impact-washington-dc-photos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eefforts%20to%20change%20the%20capital%3C%2Fa%3E's%20image%20during%20his%20second%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20country's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F250-bill-donald-trump-face-treasury-secretary-prepared-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E250th%20birthday%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20administration%20took%20an%20expedited%20approach%20to%20the%20renovation%2C%20awarding%20no-bid%20contracts%20after%20arguing%20that%20a%20full%20procurement%20process%20would%20prevent%20the%20National%20Park%20Service%20from%20reopening%20the%20pool%20in%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20the%20administration%20said%20the%20renovation%20would%20cost%20%241.8%20million%2C%20but%20federal%20records%20later%20revealed%20its%20contracts%20totaled%20%2414.8%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Cultural%20Landscape%20Foundation%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20that%20advocates%20for%20the%20preservation%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-and-worst-national-parks-traveler-who-visited-all-63-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehistoric%20landscapes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20challenged%20the%20renovation%20in%20court%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20administration%20altered%20the%20historic%20site%20without%20completing%20the%20required%20preservation%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20also%20faced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquiet-luxury-loud-tacky-wealth-america-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eaesthetic%20criticism%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20nonprofit%20leaders%20saying%20the%20renovation%20undermined%20the%20landmark's%20historical%20significance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20supposed%20to%20look%20like%20you're%20going%20to%20dive%20in%20and%20swim%2C%26quot%3B%20Judy%20Scott%20Feldman%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20National%20Mall%20Coalition%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20that%20helps%20protect%20the%20capital's%20cultural%20legacy%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2026%2F05%2F18%2Fpolitics%2Freflecting-pool-trump-paint%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20CNN%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIt%20wasn't%20intended%20as%20a%20place%20that%20looks%20jolly%20like%20your%20local%20golf%20course.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Interior%20Department%20said%20the%20blue%20surface%20would%20improve%20the%20pool's%20reflection%20and%20%26quot%3Benhance%20the%20visitor%20experience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20won't%20leak%2C%20it%20will%20shine%2C%20and%20be%20the%20pride%20of%20Washington%20DC%20for%20decades%20to%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20wrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20Truth%20Social.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flincoln-reflecting-pool-green-again-after-renovation-photos-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781725363000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a318fa32bbd1d834ef24309%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flincoln-reflecting-pool-green-again-after-renovation-photos-2026-6%22%