%20%24135%2C%20jumped%20as%20high%20as%20%24218%20this%20week%2C%20up%2061%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20level%20might%20mark%20the%20peak%20for%20a%20while%2C%20with%20warning%20signs%20that%20a%20larger%20decline%20may%20already%20be%20in%20motion%2C%20Meeks%20says.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-spcx-stock-lockup-period-expire-nasdaq-elon-musk-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESpaceX%20shares%3C%2Fa%3E%20tumbled%20as%20much%20as%203%25%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20estimated%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-stock-price-overvalued-ipo-starship-rocket-data-centers-morningstar-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efair%20value%20for%20the%20stock%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20about%20a%20third%20of%20where%20shares%20were%20trading%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20implying%20a%20decline%20to%20%2463%20a%20share%2C%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview%2C%20a%20drop%20of%20nearly%2070%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20think%20that%20we've%20seen%20the%20top%2C%26quot%3B%20Meeks%20said%2C%20though%20he%20noted%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20tell%20due%20to%20the%20extreme%20speculative%20hype%20surrounding%20SpaceX.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20investing%20in%20the%20Elon%20Musk%20cult.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWall%20Street%20has%20been%20wary%20of%20a%20potential%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-stock-price-outlook-after-ipo-market-bull-bear-cases-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edecline%20in%20SpaceX%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20given%20the%20speculative%20fervor%20that's%20fueled%20its%20IPO%20and%20the%20general%20trend%20of%20IPOs%20fizzling%20out%20after%20the%20lock-up%20periods%20expire%20and%20insiders%20start%20dumping%20the%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpaceX%20has%20a%20staggered%20lockup%20expiration%20schedule%20over%20the%20coming%20months%2C%20but%20Meeks%20said%20he%20sees%20several%20signs%20the%20decline%20could%20come%20before%20then.%20He%20pointed%20to%20options-implied%20volatility%20for%20SpaceX%2C%20which%20clocked%20in%20at%2097.5%25%20on%20Wednesday.%20That%20means%20investors%20are%20bracing%20for%20the%20possibility%20for%20the%20stock%20to%20see%20a%2097%25%20move%20in%20either%20direction%20in%20the%20coming%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20level%20of%20volatility%20is%20extreme%20even%20by%20mega-cap%20IPO%20standards%2C%20Meeks%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stock's%20options-implied%20volatility%20also%20outstrips%20that%20of%20the%20other%20Magnificent%20Seven%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fils8J%2F2%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Options-implied%20volatility%20for%20SpaceX%2C%20the%20Mag%207%20stocks%2C%20and%20the%20S%26amp%3Bamp%3BP%20500%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22324%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ESpaceX's%20fundamentals%20are%20also%20troubling%2C%20Meeks%20added.%20The%20firm%20recorded%20a%20net%20loss%20of%20%244.9%20billion%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20near-term%20catalysts%20he%20said%20risk%20sparking%20a%20decline%20in%20SpaceX%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221bab35d7-ddc2-42de-b6fd-80a78db106dd%5C%22%3E1.%20SpaceX%20issues%20more%20shares%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESpaceX%20sold%20less%20than%205%25%20of%20shares%20for%20the%20public%20to%20trade%2C%20creating%20a%20scarcity%20effect%20that%20helps%20prop%20up%20the%20price.%20That%20effect%20will%20dissipate%20should%20SpaceX%20decide%20to%20issue%20more%20public%20stock%2C%20Meeks%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpaceX%20hasn't%20announced%20any%20official%20plans%20to%20issue%20more%20stock%2C%20though%20its%20amended%20S-1%20filing%20includes%20a%20note%20that%20says%20the%20company%20could%20issue%20more%20shares%20in%20the%20future%20for%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2FArchives%2Fedgar%2Fdata%2F1181412%2F000162828026036936%2Fspaceexplorationtechnologi.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20variety%20of%20corporate%20purposes%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-spcx-stock-free-float-volatility-elon-musk-nasdaq-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESpaceX's%20public%20float%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20measure%20of%20how%20much%20of%20the%20company%20is%20available%20for%20public%20trading%2C%20is%204%25.%20Nvidia%2C%20by%20comparison%2C%20has%20a%20public%20float%20of%2096%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d4bdd541-6a2e-4678-b43d-daf5eee91f2b%5C%22%3E2.%20AI%20hype%20dies%20down%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESpaceX%20is%20an%20AI%20play%2C%20and%20investors%20are%20pricing%20in%20big%20moves%20down%20the%20line%20related%20to%20the%20technology%2C%20including%20orbital%20data%20centers%20to%20capture%20more%20of%20the%20market%20for%20AI%20compute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20basis%20of%20this%20AI%20company%20is%20xAI%2C%20which%20has%20not%20been%20very%20successful%2C%26quot%3B%20Meeks%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20SpaceX's%20%246.4%20billion%20loss%20in%20its%20AI%20business%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20more%20about%20what%20people%20feel%20about%20the%20AI%20theme%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%20for%20the%20stock's%20future%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f73e0c17-8257-4004-a901-e4d0c8941025%5C%22%3E3.%20SpaceX%20earnings%20fall%20short%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20are%20expecting%20SpaceX's%20first%20earnings%20report%20as%20a%20public%20company%20sometime%20in%20August%2C%20just%20before%20the%20first%20wave%20of%20its%20insider%20lock-ups%20will%20expire.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20investors%20will%20have%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20pay%20attention%20to%20how%20its%20valuation%20isn't%20squaring%20with%20fundamentals%2C%20Meeks%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%2