ws.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fthe-14-point-us-iran-deal-what-is-in-it-13555121%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20has%20signed%20a%20deal%20aimed%20at%20ending%20the%20war%20with%20Iran.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fthe-14-point-us-iran-deal-what-is-in-it-13555121%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20spent%20%24750%20on%20a%20World%20Cup%20ticket%20to%20see%20Scotland%20play.%20Days%20later%20StubHub%20said%20it%20wasn't%20available%20anymore.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20posing%20with%20outfit%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3298f2564c774507cd3632%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKatherine%20Howe%20bought%20a%20skirt%20to%20see%20Scotland%20play%20at%20the%20World%20Cup.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Katherine%20Howe%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EKatherine%20Howe%20is%20a%2049-year-old%20author%20in%20Marblehead%2C%20Massachusetts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHowe%20bought%20a%20ticket%20to%20Scotland%20versus%20Morocco%20in%20Boston%20on%20StubHub.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20four%20days%20before%20the%20game%2C%20she%20was%20informed%20that%20her%20ticket%20was%20no%20longer%20available.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.katherinehowe.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EKatherine%20Howe%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3Ea%20historian%20and%20novelist.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20I%20opened%20my%20emails%20to%20find%20that%20my%20ticket%20to%20the%20Scotland%20versus%20Morocco%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworld-cup-trip-expensive-alternative-soccer-travel-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorld%20Cup%20game%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20no%20longer%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20this%20ticket%20was%20years%20in%20the%20making.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201994%2C%20I%20watched%20my%20first-ever%20World%20Cup%20game%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-united-states-to-brazil-differences-surprising-things-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eliving%20in%20Brazil%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20was%20in%20a%20small%2C%20rural%20town%20with%20lots%20of%20local%20Brazilians%20watching%20on%20a%20small%20TV.%20Everyone%20went%20wild%20when%20Brazil%20actually%20won%20the%20entire%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20Americans%20at%20the%20time%2C%20I%20wasn't%20aware%20that%20the%20World%20Cup%20even%20existed%2C%20but%20I%20imbibed%20the%20excitement%20and%20passion%20for%20the%20tournament%20while%20in%20Brazil%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Cup%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20global%20phenomena.%20It%20breaks%20barriers%20%E2%80%94%20with%20everyone%20from%20all%20around%20the%20world%20getting%20involved.%20Even%20countries%20as%20small%20as%20Cura%C3%A7ao%20can%20take%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I'm%20not%20a%20regular%20soccer%20fan%2C%20I%20became%20a%20World%20Cup%20fan%20in%201994.%20Four%20years%20later%2C%20I%20was%20in%20Paris%20when%20the%20World%20Cup%20was%20held%20there.%20It%20was%20the%20last%20year%20Scotland%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworld-cup-team-blames-fifa-travel-chaos-plane-mixup-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equalified%20for%20the%20World%20Cup%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%202026.%20I%20have%20vivid%20memories%20of%20the%20streets%20of%20Paris%20being%20flooded%20with%20people%20in%20kilts%2C%20having%20the%20time%20of%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20couldn't%20afford%20to%20go%20to%20the%20matches%2C%20but%20again%2C%20I%20loved%20the%20togetherness%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffifa-world-cup-hydration-breaks-critics-say-excuse-for-commercials-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epassion%20of%20the%20tournament%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229a71aaa2-e765-4a2f-90c1-931b75c86713%5C%22%3EFast%20forward%2028%20years%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20out%20that%20the%20World%20Cup%20was%20happening%20in%20the%20United%20States%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20something%20that%20hadn't%20been%20on%20my%20radar%20previously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20consider%20looking%20for%20tickets%20%E2%80%94%20unaware%20that%20games%20would%20be%20in%20Boston%2C%20only%20about%20an%20hour%20away%20from%20where%20I%20live%20in%20Massachusetts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20weekend%2C%20on%20Saturday%2C%20I%20was%20at%20the%20Boston%20train%20station%20when%20I%20suddenly%20saw%20all%20these%20men%20in%20kilts.%20It%20suddenly%20clicked%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworld-cup-scotland-fan-group-tartan-army-providence-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EScotland%20was%20playing%20Haiti%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Boston%20later%20that%20day.%20It%20felt%20like%20I%20had%20been%20transported%20back%20to%20Paris%2028%20years%20ago%2C%20with%20Scottish%20accents%20and%20tartan%20surrounding%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20immediately%20started%20searching%20for%20where%20they%20were%20playing%20next%20and%20where%20I%20could%20get%20a%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20game%20was%20on%20June%2019%20in%20Boston.%20I%20could%20do%20that%20date.%20I%20could%20do%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20naively%20(I've%20never%20been%20one%20to%20go%20to%20sports%20games%20or%20big%20concerts)%2C%20I%20searched%20%26quot%3Btickets%20for%20Scotland%20versus%20Morocco%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20first%20site%20that%20came%20up%20was%20StubHub.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ccc08675-b618-4c18-9f8f-f71eac0c29da%5C%22%3EI%20bought%20a%20%24750%20ticket%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20the%20cheapest%20ticket%20at%20%24750.%20That%20was%20really%20expensive%20for%20me%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%20and%20I%20would%20notice%20the%20amount%20being%20deducted%20from%20my%20bank%20account%2C%20but%20I%20really%20wanted%20to%20see%20this%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20bought%20it.%20I%20got%20my%20email%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstubhub-dynamic-pricing-experiment-fees-ticket-costs-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econfirmation%20from%20StubHub%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20was%20going%20to%20see%20Scotland%20in%20the%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22686%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22StubHub%20email%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a32b9f32bbd1d834ef249ed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22308%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKatherine%20Howe%20received%20an%20email%20from%20StubHub%20saying%20that%20her%20ticket%20was%20no%20longer%20available.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Katherine%20Howe%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20preparation%20for%20the%20game%2C%20I%20ordered%20a%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscottish-traditions-i-grew-up-with-that-americans-find-surprising-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20tartan%20skirt%3C%2Fa%3E%20(with%20pockets%20for%20my%20phone).%20I%20was%20ready%20and%20raring%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20on%20Monday%2C%20I%20got%20that%20dreadful%2C%20disappointing%20email%20that%20the%20ticket%20wasn't%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a8763009-9bae-4719-8ccb-fa08410c8cff%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20was%20given%20the%20option%20to%20choose%20another%20ticket%2C%20but%20there%20are%20none%20left%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20email%2C%20I%20was%20instructed%20to%20click%20a%20link%20that%20would%20take%20me%20to%20a%20website%20to%20pick%20another%20comparable%20ticket%3B%20however%2C%20when%20I%20got%20to%20this%20website%2C%20I%20could%20only%20click%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstubhub-refund-75k-customers-for-canceled-events-in-pandemic-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erefund%20option%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnbeknownst%20to%20me%2C%20StubHub%20is%20a%20marketplace%20%E2%80%94%20they%20don't%20own%20the%20tickets%3B%20they%20simply%20allow%20people%20to%20sell%20them%20on%20their%20website.%20What%20I'm%20guessing%20happened%20is%20that%20someone%20pledged%20to%20sell%20that%20ticket%20I%20bought%2C%20but%20then%2C%20when%20Scotland%20won%20their%20first%20game%2C%20removed%20the%20ticket%20from%20StubHub%20(incurring%20a%20fine)%20so%20that%20they%20could%20resell%20it%20for%20more%20or%20use%20it%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20opened%20a%20chat%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-customer-service-profit-annoyance-economy-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecustomer%20service%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20calmly%20pleaded%20my%20case%20with%20the%20representative.%20Eventually%2C%20I%20was%20told%20to%20%26quot%3Bhold%20tight%26quot%3B%20until%20one%20hour%20before%20the%20game%2C%20and%20that%20tickets%20might%20be%20released%20then.%20That%2C%20of%20course%2C%20isn't%20going%20to%20work.%20I%20have%20to%20buy%20a%20special%20train%20ticket%20to%20get%20to%20the%20game%2C%20and%20to%20buy%20that%20train%20ticket%2C%20I%20need%20a%20ticket%20to%20the%20game.%20It%20would%20all%20take%20much%20longer%20than%20just%20one%20hour%20to%20get%20from%20my%20house%20to%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERefusing%20to%20back%20down%2C%20I%20have%20not%20yet%20accepted%20a%20refund%2C%20hopeful%20I%20will%20be%20given%20a%20ticket%2C%20the%20ticket%20I%20already%20paid%20for.%20I%20was%20looking%20forward%20to%20this%20game%20%E2%80%94%20a%20once-in-a-lifetime%20opportunity%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20I'll%20be%20watching%20either%20way.%20Go%20Scotland!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEditor's%20note%3A%20When%20reached%20out%20for%20comment%2C%20StubHub%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20understand%20that%20attending%20the%20World%20Cup%20represents%20a%20significant%20investment%20in%20time%20and%20money%2C%20and%20we%20take%20our%20responsibility%20to%20every%20fan%20who%20books%20through%20our%20platform%20seriously.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMany%20of%20the%20issues%20fans%20are%20facing%20trace%20back%20to%20the%20event%20organizer's%20technology%20infrastructure%2C%20newly%20announced%20transfer%20restrictions%2C%20and%20a%20new%20app%20that%20was%20launched%20just%20a%20month%20ago%20ahead%20of%20such%20a%20major%20event.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3ERegardless%20of%20the%20cause%2C%20when%20sellers%20don't%20deliver%20tickets%20on%20time%2C%20StubHub%20investigates%20and%20takes%20swift%20action%20in%20line%20with%20our%20terms%20%26amp%3B%20conditions%2C%20including%20permanent%20bans%20and%20financial%20penalties.%20Every%20order%20on%20StubHub%20is%20backed%20by%20our%20FanProtect%20Guarantee%2C%20which%20provides%20alternative%20tickets%20or%20a%20full%20refund.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworld-cup-ticket-disappeared-after-purchase-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781723281000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3298f2564c774507cd3632%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworld-cup-ticket-disappeared-after-purchase-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Katherine%20Howe%20says%20she%20bought%20a%20ticket%20to%20see%20Scotland%20at%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20only%20to%20learn%20days%20later%20it%20was%20unavailable.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Lauren%20Crosby%20Medlicott)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ex-Nigeria%20oil%20minister%20cleared%20in%20UK%20bribery%20trial%22%2C