22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fworld-news%2Ffed-begins-warsh-era-by-keeping-rates-on-hold-sees-a-hike-later-this-year-126061800002_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20'anti-bot'%20startup%20wants%20to%20pay%20you%20to%20interact%20with%20brands.%20Read%20the%20pitch%20deck%20it%20used%20to%20raise%20%2418.5%20million.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22EarnOS%20founder%20and%20CEO%20Phil%20George%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a31cbea564c774507cd33c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEarnOS%20founder%20and%20CEO%20Phil%20George.%3Cp%3EEarnOS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EEarnOS%20has%20launched%20an%20app%20to%20help%20brands%20get%20engagement%20from%20verified%20humans%20rather%20than%20AI%20bots.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20startup%20pays%20rewards%20for%20users%20who%20engage%20with%20brands%20on%20its%20app.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBusiness%20Insider%20got%20an%20exclusive%20look%20at%20the%20pitch%20deck%20it%20used%20to%20secure%20%2418.5%20million%20in%20funding.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEarnOS%2C%20a%20startup%20that%20pays%20people%20to%20interact%20with%20brands%20online%20to%20ensure%20they%20are%20seen%20by%20humans%20and%20not%20AI%20bots%2C%20has%20raised%20%2418.5%20million%20in%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20New%20York-based%20company%20launched%20its%20app%2C%20Ero%2C%20where%20customers%20can%20verify%20they%20are%20human%20and%20earn%20rewards%20for%20engaging%20with%20a%20brand's%20content.%20Users%20can%20scroll%20through%20the%20Ero%20app%20feed%20and%20participate%20in%20challenges%2C%20such%20as%20physical%20activities%20tracked%20through%20their%20fitness%20app%2C%20share%20their%20data%2C%20and%20click%20on%20brand%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrands%20only%20pay%20when%20someone%20engages%20with%20them%2C%20and%20the%20app%20helps%20them%20to%20ensure%20humans%2C%20and%20not%20AI%20bots%2C%20are%20seeing%20their%20content%2C%20Phil%20George%2C%20the%20startup's%20CEO%20and%20founder%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20entirety%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadvertising-dead-mastercard-senior-fellow-art-of-marketing-raja-rajamannar-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eadvertising%20online%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20envisaged%20at%20a%20time%20where%20the%20assumption%20was%20that%20everyone%20online%20was%20a%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20George%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20dynamic%20has%20changed%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcpg-marketers-using-ai-ad-testing-to-video-production-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erise%20of%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20month%2C%20Cloudflare%2C%20a%20network%20service%20firm%2C%20said%20that%20website%20traffic%20from%20bots%20had%20overtaken%20human%20activity%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeorge%20positions%20EarnOS%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Banti-bot%26quot%3B%20company%20that's%20trying%20to%20help%20build%20a%20%26quot%3Bverified%20internet.%26quot%3B%20It%20is%20also%20pitching%20itself%20as%20an%20alternative%20digital%20advertising%20app%20to%20Google%20or%20Facebook%2C%20which%20rely%20on%20clicks%20and%20impressions%20that%20can%20sometimes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-bots-strip-mining-web-anthropic-leads-ethical-claude-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einclude%20bot%20activity%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThink%20of%20it%20as%20a%20loyalty%20program%20for%20who%20you%20are%20as%20a%20person%20rather%20than%20as%20a%20particular%20brand%2C%26quot%3B%20George%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarnOS%20takes%20a%20cut%20of%20the%20brand's%20ad%20spend%20on%20the%20app%2C%20with%20the%20remainder%20%E2%80%94%20up%20to%2075%25%20of%20every%20dollar%20%E2%80%94%20going%20to%20users%20who%20complete%20tasks%20with%20brands%20on%20the%20app%2C%20George%20said.%20The%20app%20distributes%20rewards%20in%20the%20USD%20stablecoin%20cryptocurrency%2C%20which%20users%20can%20then%20spend%20with%20merchants%20in%20dollars%20via%20an%20EarnOS%20Visa%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarnOS%20said%20the%20app%20has%20launched%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20US%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20Australia%2C%20with%20a%20%2430%20million%20annualized%20rewards%20pool%20funded%20by%20participating%20brands%20across%20industries%20such%20as%20ride-hailing%2C%20retail%2C%20streaming%2C%20and%20consumer%20finance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20ran%20a%20beta%20test%20of%20the%20service%20from%20March%202025%20through%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%20EarnOS%20said%20it%20partnered%20with%20152%20brands%2C%20had%203%20million%20signups%2C%20and%20paid%20out%20%2450%2C000%20in%20rewards%20during%20this%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlready%2C%20it's%20working%20with%20brands%20like%20Nike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarnOS%20creates%20an%20opportunity%20to%20make%20brand%20interactions%20fun%2C%20participatory%2C%20and%20transparent%2C%20and%20to%20get%20away%20from%20AI%20slop%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20John%20Shiel%2C%20senior%20content%20and%20engagement%20manager%20at%20Nike%20Innovation%20Labs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestment%20firm%201kx%20led%20its%20%246%20million%20round%2C%20with%20participation%20from%20Coinbase%20Ventures%2C%20Circle%20Ventures%2C%20and%20Social%20Graph%20Ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20remaining%20%2412.5%20million%20financing%20comes%20from%20Verona%2C%20which%20EarnOs%20will%20get%20over%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeorge%20said%20the%20company%20plans%20to%20use%20the%20funding%20to%20expand%20into%20new%20markets%20later%20this%20year%20as%20bot%20activity%20soars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20internet%20is%20going%20to%20get%20worse%20before%20it%20gets%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EHere's%20an%20exclusive%20look%20at%20the%2024-page%20pitch%20deck%20EarnOS%20used%20during%20the%20fundraising%20process%20to%20secure%20%2418.5%20million.%20Some%20commercially%20sensitive%20slides%20have%20been%20omitted.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22EarnOS%20pitch%20deck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a32d1032bbd1d834ef24c3f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EEarnOS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22EarnOS%20pitch%20deck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a32d1014074dae0e2044cc8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EEarnOS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22EarnOS%20pitch%20deck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a32d1032bbd1d834ef24c3c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EEarnOS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22EarnOS%20pitch%20deck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a32d1034074dae0e2044cd6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EEarnOS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22EarnOS%20pitch%20deck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a32d1014074dae0e2044ccb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EEarnOS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22EarnOS%20pitch%20deck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a32d102