er%20100%20years%2C%20fewer%20than%2030%20students%20are%20admitted%20each%20year%20%E2%80%94%20and%20none%20of%20them%20pay%20tuition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222cdfb290-c554-44ab-a775-f5d64d54b078%5C%22%3EOnly%205%25%20of%20applicants%20are%20accepted%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224373%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Outside%20view%20of%20the%20Curtis%20Institute%20of%20Music%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a32c6004074dae0e2044b47%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOutside%20view%20of%20the%20Curtis%20Institute%20building%20in%20Philadelphia.%3Cp%3EPaul%20Marotta%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20year%2C%20the%20Curtis%20Institute%20receives%20over%20500%20applications%2C%20but%20only%205%25%20are%20admitted%2C%20according%20to%20the%20most%20recent%20data%20from%20the%20National%20Center%20for%20Education%20Statistics'%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnces.ed.gov%2Fcollegenavigator%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECollege%20Navigator%20tool%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Business%20Insider%20looked%20at%20the%20hardest%20schools%20to%20get%20into%2C%20based%20on%20their%20admissions%20rate%20for%20the%202024-2025%20school%20year%2C%20Curtis%20ranked%2014th%20in%20the%20nation%2C%20placing%20it%20ahead%20of%20Duke%2C%20Johns%20Hopkins%2C%20and%20Cornell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20school%20admits%20the%20same%20percentage%20of%20applicants%20as%20the%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20although%20it%20has%20a%20much%20smaller%20applicant%20pool%20and%20fewer%20seats%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20school%20ensures%20that%2C%20at%20any%20given%20point%2C%20it%20has%20just%20around%20160%20students%2C%20enough%20to%20fill%20a%20full%20symphony%20orchestra%20and%20opera%2C%20along%20with%20select%20musicians%20in%20piano%2C%20guitar%2C%20composition%2C%20conducting%2C%20and%20organ%2C%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.