via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAnthropic%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdario-amodei%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDario%20Amodei%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20trust%20was%20at%20the%20core%20of%20his%20decision%20to%20famously%20leave%20OpenAI%20and%20Sam%20Altman.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20argue%20with%20someone%20when%20you%20don't%20have%20the%20same%20vision%20and%20you%20don't%20trust%20them%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20an%20apparent%20jab%20at%20Altman.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAmodei%20said%20he%20does%20find%20others%20in%20AI%20%26quot%3Btrustworthy%2C%26quot%3B%20citing%20his%20relationship%20with%20Google%20DeepMind%20CEO%20Demis%20Hassabis.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20CEO%20Dario%20Amodei%20said%20he's%20at%20%26quot%3Bpeace%26quot%3B%20with%20where%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-dario-amodei-anthropic-openai-rivalry-timeline-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthropic-OpenAI%20rivalry%3C%2Fa%3E%20stands%20even%20as%20a%20cold%20war%20brews%20between%20two%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20AI%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20did%20throw%20some%20shade%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E's%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20why%20argue%20with%20someone%20when%20you%20don't%20have%20the%20same%20vision%20and%20you%20don't%20trust%20them%3F%26quot%3B%20Amodei%20said%20in%20an%20apparent%20jab%20at%20the%20OpenAI%20CEO%20during%20a%20lengthy%20Bloomberg%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dx2VHFgyawPE%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20%26quot%3BThe%20Circuit%20with%20Emily%20Chang%26quot%3B%20published%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20to%20resolve%20it%20is%20you%20go%20off%20and%20do%20your%20thing%2C%20they%20go%20off%20and%20do%20their%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20am%20completely%20at%20peace%20with%20the%20idea%20that%20we're%20doing%20things%20our%20way%20and%20they're%20doing%20things%20their%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20someone%20else%20will%20decide%20who%20was%20right%2C%20Amodei%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe'll%20see%20who%20wins%20in%20the%20market%20and%20we'll%20see%20who%20wins%20in%20the%20court%20of%20public%20opinion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20those%20things%20speak%20louder%20than%20any%20drama%20about%20why%20who%20left%20what.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Chang%20told%20Amodei%2C%20the%20story%20behind%20why%20he%2C%20his%20sister%20Daniela%2C%20and%20nine%20OpenAI%20employees%20left%20in%202020%20to%20start%20Anthropic%20has%20become%20Silicon%20Valley%20%26quot%3Blore.%26quot%3B%20Once%20the%20underdog%2C%20Anthropic%20is%20now%20widely%20viewed%20as%20having%20overtaken%20OpenAI%20in%20the%20generative%20AI%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmodei's%20exit%20has%20received%20renewed%20attention%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newyorker.com%2Fmagazine%2F2026%2F04%2F13%2Fsam-altman-may-control-our-future-can-he-be-trusted%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERonan%20Farrow's%20expos%C3%A9%20in%20The%20New%20Yorker%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20examined%20whether%20Altman%20could%20be%20trusted.%20Amodei's%20contemporaneous%20notes%2C%20which%20he%20took%20about%20his%20interactions%20with%20Altman%20during%20his%20time%20at%20OpenAI%2C%20are%20cited%20throughout%20the%20report.%20Days%20after%20the%20report's%20publication%2C%20Altman's%20home%20was%20attacked%2C%20an%20incident%20he%20partially%20blamed%20on%20The%20New%20Yorker%20report%20(without%20naming%20the%20publication%20directly)%2C%20and%20later%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-attack-on-home-anthropic-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehow%20Anthropic%20talks%20about%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20doomerism%20talk%20hasn't%20helped.%20I%20think%20the%20way%20certain%20other%20labs%20talk%20about%20us%20hasn't%20helped%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20said%20during%20an%20April%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BCore%20Memory%26quot%3B%20podcast%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20way%20Anthropic%20talks%20about%20OpenAI%20doesn't%20help.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmodei%20chalked%20up%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-leaders-india-summit-awkward-photo-hands-modi-altman-amodei-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emost%20viral%20moment%20in%20his%20rivalry%20with%20Altman%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20the%20pair%20notably%20declined%20to%20join%20their%20fellow%20industry%20leaders%20in%20a%20show%20of%20unity%2C%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bextreme%20disorganization%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20India%20AI%20summit.%20The%20Anthropic%20CEO%20said%20other%20summits%20featuring%20world%20leaders%20are%20often%20a%20mess%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20to%20tell%20you%2C%20OK%3F%20There%20was%20like%20Narendra%20Modi%20up%20there%20suddenly%20telling%20everyone%20to%20hold%20hands%2C%26quot%3B%20Amodei%20said%20of%20the%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20who%20was%20positioned%20right%20next%20to%20Altman%20and%20Amodei.%20(Left%20unsaid%20is%20that%20both%20Altman%20and%20Amodei%20held%20hands%20with%20the%20other%20people%20next%20to%20them.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sam%20Altman%20and%20Dario%20Amodei%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6996cc27f8731049f3af5fdb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESam%20Altman%20and%20Dario%20Amodei's%20hands%20did%20not%20make%20contact.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20internet%20noticed.%3Cp%3ELudovic%20MARIN%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20did%20not%20name%20Altman%20directly%2C%20Amodei%20appeared%20to%20implicitly%20criticize%20OpenAI%20on%20multiple%20occasions%20during%20his%20over%201-hour%20interview%20with%20Chang.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20how%20the%20world%20could%20trust%20AI%20companies%20to%20cooperate%20on%20major%20AI%20safety%20issues%2C%20Amodei%20suggested%20it%20was%20less%20about%20everyone%20getting%20along%20and%20more%20about%20who%20sets%20the%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20think%20needs%20to%20happen%20is%20that%20the%20trustworthy%20actors%20need%20to%20get%20together%20and%20put%20the%20untrustworthy%20actors%20in%20a%20position%20where%20they%20kind%20of%20have%20to%20adopt%20the%20same%20standards%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWith%20a%20lot%20of%20experience%2C%20I've%20learned%20that%20there%20are%20some%20folks%20who%20don't%20do%20the%20right%20thing%20on%20their%20own%2C%20but%20if%20there's%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20industry%20that's%20doing%20the%20right%20thing%2C%20then%20I%20think%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20industry%20is%20kind%20of%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20left%20in%20a%20position%20where%20there's%20not%20much%20they%20can%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmodei%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20narrative%20that%20%26quot%3Bno%20one%20trusts%20each%20other%26quot%3B%20in%20AI%20isn't%20true%2C%20citing%20his%20relationship%20with%20Google%20DeepMind%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-demis-hassabis-deepmind-founder-ai-google-nobel-prize-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDemis%20Hassabis.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20known%20him%20for%2015%20years.%20We've%20worked%20together%20on%20a%20number%20of%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20Amodei%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20buy%20compute%20from%20Google.%20We%20swap%20safety%20ideas%20all%20the%20time.%20So%20my%20view%20of%20this%20is%20that%20one%2C%20there%20are%20some%20players%20who%20are%20more%20trustworthy%20than%20others%2C%20and%20I%20think%20there%20are%20players%20outside%20Anthropic%20who%20I%20trust%2C%20who%20I%20see%20as%20trustworthy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-dario-amodei-does-not-trust-sam-altman-openai-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781718245000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a32c7ec564c774507cd388f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-dario-amodei-does-not-trust-sam-altman-openai-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anthropic%20CEO%20Dario%20Amodei%2C%20who%20famously%20left%20OpenAI%20in%202020%2C%20says%20he's%20%26quot%3Bat%20peace%26quot%3B%20on%20where%20things%20stand%20with%20his%20chief%20AI%20rival.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bgriffiths%40insider.com%20(Brent%20D.%20Griffiths)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A94%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Nobody%20did%20that%20on%20purpose%E2%80%99%3A%20Trump%20says%20Iran%20girls%E2%80%99%20school%20bombing%20was%20not%20deliberate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1781718100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131808379%2Cimgsize-826117.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fnobody-did-that-on-purpose-trump-says-iran-girls-school-bombing-was-not-deliberate%2Farticleshow%2F131808160.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F131808160.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fnobody-did-that-on-purpose-trum