d%20support%20biodiversity.%20Vishal%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CTrees%20improve%20soil%20moisture%2C%20reduce%20evaporation%2C%20and%20create%20micro-channels%20that%20hold%20rainwater.%20An%20acre%20of%20forest%20can%20save%20over%2012%20million%20litres%20of%20water%20annually%20compared%20to%20conventional%20paddy%20fields.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGurpreet%20reinforces%20the%20connection%3A%20%E2%80%9CWater%20and%20trees%20are%20intertwined.%20By%20protecting%20one%2C%20we%20safeguard%20the%20other.%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20future%20depends%20on%20this%20balance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWho%20owns%20a%20mini%20forest%3F%20The%20power%20of%20local%20pride%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20balance%20is%20being%20rebuilt%20not%20through%20imposition%20but%20collaboration.%20Much%20of%20the%20land%20is%20government-owned%2C%20but%20when%20individuals%20like%20Inderjit%20offer%20private%20land%2C%20it%20fosters%20co-ownership%20and%20responsibility.%20%E2%80%9CVillages%20take%20ownership%2C%20and%20that%20is%20why%20survival%20rates%20of%20trees%20are%20so%20high%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vishal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20many%20places%2C%20schools%20are%20involved%2C%20turning%20forests%20into%20living%20classrooms%20where%20children%20learn%20about%20ecology%20and%20conservation.%20%E2%80%9CChildren%20see%20the%20trees%20grow%20and%20learn%20to%20respect%20nature%2C%E2%80%9D%20Inderjit%20smiles.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20plants%20seeds%20of%20awareness%20that%20will%20last%20generations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20planting%20a%20few%20saplings%20in%20one%20village%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Billion%20Tree%20Project%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20grown%20into%20a%20statewide%20movement%20spanning%2017%20districts.%20Each%20of%20the%20three%20million%20trees%20has%20been%20carefully%20tracked%2C%20with%20survival%20rates%20monitored%20through%20rigorous%20documentation%20and%20local%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5