e%20in%20regular%20attendance%2C%20from%20fewer%20than%2030%20to%20100%20students%20within%20a%20month%20of%20her%20intensive%20community%20engagement.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1-1757060631.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1-1757060631-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1-1757060631-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1-1757060631-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1-1757060631-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496798%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHer%20efforts%20resulted%20in%20a%20rise%20in%20regular%20attendance%2C%20from%20fewer%20than%2030%20to%20100%20students%20within%20a%20month%20of%20her%20intensive%20community%20engagement.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20empty%20classrooms%20to%20crowded%20mornings%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20day%20begins%20before%20dawn.%20By%208%20AM%2C%20Sangeeta%20is%20already%20at%20the%20school%20gate%2C%20greeting%20children%20who%20walk%20in%20barefoot%2C%20their%20satchels%20bouncing%20against%20their%20backs.%20The%20sight%20warms%20her%20now%2C%20but%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20always%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COut%20of%20130%20children%20enrolled%2C%20fewer%20than%2030%20attended%20regularly%20when%20I%20first%20joined%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20remembers%20her%20frustration.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20just%20sit%20inside%20the%20classroom%20and%20wait.%20So%20after%20school%20hours%2C%20I%20would%20go%20door%20to%20door%20in%20the%20afternoons.%20I%20sat%20with%20parents%2C%20explained%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%