0631.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D496794%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Twelve%20years%20ago%2C%20Sangeeta%20Maurya%20cried%20at%20her%20posting%20in%20Raebareli%20when%20only%2030%20of%20130%20students%20turned%20up.%20Today%2C%20through%20stories%2C%20songs%2C%20and%20compassion%2C%20she%20has%20filled%20her%20classrooms%20with%20laughter%20and%20hope%20%E2%80%94%20proving%20that%20teaching%20in%20villages%20is%20more%20than%20a%20job.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F496794%2Fa-day-in-the-life-of-rural-school-teacher-raebareli-uttar-pradesh-sangeeta-maurya%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20More%20Parents%20Are%20Adding%20Millets%20%26amp%3B%20Microgreens%20to%20Their%20Kids%E2%80%99%20Lunchboxes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFeature%20image%20courtesy%3A%20Sanchita%20Daswani%2F%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2Fimage-photo%2Fgreen-organic-raw-microgreen-sprouts-ready-2452650587%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20Monday%20morning%2C%20a%20seven-year-old%20opens%20his%20tiffin%20box%20in%20school.%20Inside%20are%20bright%20orange%20millet%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20small%20tub%20of%20chutney%2C%20and%20a%20sprinkling%20of%20microgreens%20shaped%20like%20bunny%20ears.%20He%20beams%20as%20his%20friends%20crowd%20around%2C%20curious.%20In%20another%20corner%2C%20his%20classmate%20struggles%20with%20a%20packet%20of%20chips%20and%20a%20cream-filled%20biscuit%2C%20finishing%20quickly%20but%20still%20feeling%20hungry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20little%20lunchbox%20stories%20play%20out%20in%20schools%20across%20India%20every%20day.%20For%20many%20parents%2C%20convenience%20often%20trumps%20nutrition%20in%20the%20rush%20of%20mornings.%20Y